Nick Stockton is a senior at the University of Cincinnati in the Aerospace Engineering program. He fell in love with fuzzy logic and eveolutionary algorithms in his sophomore year and hasn't stopped fiddling since. He is becoming a passable RC pilot with fewer uncontrolled descents every day. He is currently finishing his undergraduate education and transitioning deriectly into a master's of science in Aerospace with an emphasis in dynaics and controls.
